data.description: This charming ranch home is perfectly situated just minutes away from the vibrant Marietta Square and I75, perfect for a first time home buyer or an investor. Step inside and be greeted by the warm and inviting atmosphere of this cozy updated home. The spacious living area is bathed in natural light, creating a cozy and comfortable space for relaxation and entertainment. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it ideal for hosting gatherings with family and friends. Step outside and discover your own private oasis. The backyard is perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply unwinding after a long day. The possibilities are endless with this spacious and well-maintained yard. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own an updated ranch home in Marietta without without the restrictions of an HOA. Schedule your showing today and make this house your new home sweet home.
